      <li> <a href="fields.cfm" title="A comprehensive list of majors and minors offered at Cornell"> Browse Fields of Study </a> </li> 
      <li> <a href="colleges.cfm" title="Learn more about our fourteen colleges and schools"> Browse Schools &amp; Colleges </a> </li> 
      <li> <a href="http://courses.cornell.edu/" title="Information about colleges, departments, course offerings, policies and procedures."> Browse Course Catalog </a> </li> 
     </ul> 
