         <div class="media-caption">
           Katherine Sullivan '11 traveled the Annapurna Circuit during her semester in Nepal 
         </div> 
        </div> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="callout-body"> 
       <h4 class="cu-headline"> Global Perspectives, Global Opportunities </h4> 
       <div class="callout-copy"> 
        <p> Our home is on the Hill in Ithaca, New York, but you can study just about anywhere your academic inquiries take you. </p> 
       </div> 
